url: "https://github.com/Thata-ux/dili-transcriptomic-biomarkers-xai"

abstract: >
  This repository contains the complete computational workflow for
  transcriptomic biomarker discovery of drug-induced liver injury (DILI)
  using Open TG-GATEs, explainable machine learning, SHAP interpretation,
  GO and KEGG enrichment analyses, and independent DrugMatrix validation.

keywords:
  - drug-induced liver injury
  - DILI
  - toxicogenomics
  - transcriptomics
  - explainable AI
  - XGBoost
  - SHAP
  - biomarker discovery
  - Open TG-GATEs
  - DrugMatrix

